N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 43.3 - Application

State Regulations

This Part (rule) applies throughout the State of New York
exclusively to coin-operated machines which perform or are used to perform any
manufacturing process, and to the manufacturers, owners and operators thereof, and to the places in which such machines, are exposed for
operation. Notes
